Uncover Elias' secret within the temple
The ancient coffin has brought me to some kind of ancient, sunken temple. Elias' secret hides in these forgotten depths somewhere.
The echoes of Elias' ritual mention a vessel of immortality: A piece of himself hidden here to anchor his spirit to life. If I can find that vessel, maybe I can break his enchantment.

The malignant echoes of Elias' immortality ritual still stain this place. I must destroy them.
